/docs/

# Video / reel artifacts — block instaloader/SnapInsta dumps and any large
# raw video that gets dropped into the repo for reference. The 3 marketing
# reels (mp4 versions) are exempted below since they're production assets
# referenced by the marketing + blog pages.
reel_video/
*.mp4
*.mov
*.m4v
!/public/reels/reel1.mp4
!/public/reels/reel2.mp4
!/public/reels/reel3.mp4

